---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Use | ByteLite LLC"
  description="Terms of use for the ByteLite LLC website."
  keywords="ByteLite LLC terms of use"
  
>
  <Header slot="header" />

  <section class="legal-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
      <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
      <p class="legal-sub">Last updated: May 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container legal-body">

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>This is an informational website.</h2>
        <p>The ByteLite LLC website provides information about the company, its products, and its research. It is not a store, a service portal, or an application. No products are currently for sale through this website.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Product status may change.</h2>
        <p>Product and project statuses described on this website reflect the best available information at the time of writing. No representation is made that any status is permanent or binding. ByteLite LLC may update, delay, cancel, or modify any product or project without prior notice.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Research claims are not production claims.</h2>
        <p>Research described on this website is private and ongoing. Research status does not constitute a claim of commercial readiness, public availability, or independent verification. No production infrastructure product is currently offered by ByteLite LLC.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Proprietary technology.</h2>
        <p>ByteLite LLC's research methodology and technology systems are proprietary. Nothing on this website grants any license to use, copy, or build upon ByteLite LLC's systems. Use of any ByteLite technology requires a separate license agreement.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>No warranties.</h2>
        <p>This website is provided as-is without warranty of any kind. ByteLite LLC makes no guarantee as to the accuracy, completeness, or timeliness of information provided. Use of this website is at your own risk.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Governing law.</h2>
        <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the State of Montana, USA, without regard to conflict-of-law principles.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Contact.</h2>
        <p>Legal inquiries may be directed through the <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</Layout>

<style>

.legal-hero { padding: 5rem 0 3.5rem; }
.legal-hero h1 { max-width: 480px; }
.legal-sub { margin-top: .75rem; font-size: .9375rem; color: #555e7a; }
.legal-body { max-width: 760px; }
.legal-section { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
.legal-section h2 { font-size: 1.375rem; color: #e4e7f2; margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-bottom: .75rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #1a2235; }
.legal-section h3 { font-size: 1.0625rem; color: #e4e7f2; margin: 1.5rem 0 .5rem; }
.legal-section p { font-size: .9375rem; color: #7b829e; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: .875rem; }
.legal-section a { color: #818cf8; }
.legal-section a:hover { color: #a5b4fc; }
.legal-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .625rem; }
.legal-list li { font-size: .9375rem; color: #7b829e; padding-left: 1.25rem; position: relative; line-height: 1.6; }
.legal-list li::before { content: "—"; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #4a5068; }

</style>
